Eggdrop Build Guide

Eggdrop Build Guide and FAQ

  This guide will help you successfully build and install Eggdrop using
  the Meson build system. Suggestions come from various contributors.
  If you think something should be added, please submit an issue at
  https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/issues.

  NOTE: This is not a 'quick install' guide. See the INSTALL file for
  basic setup information. This guide is intended to help you build the
  bot on uncommon operating systems or work past problems encountered
  during the build.

